<p>A <b>bedbug</b> (or <b>bed bug</b>) is a small <a href="/wiki/Nocturnal_animal" title="Nocturnal animal" class="mw-redirect">nocturnal</a> <a href="/wiki/Insect" title="Insect">insect</a> of the family <b>Cimicidae</b> that lives by <a href="/wiki/Hematophagy" title="Hematophagy">hematophagy</a>, or by feeding on the <a href="/wiki/Blood" title="Blood">blood</a> of <a href="/wiki/Human" title="Human">humans</a> and other <a href="/wiki/Homeothermic" title="Homeothermic" class="mw-redirect">warm-blooded</a> <a href="/wiki/Host_(biology)" title="Host (biology)">hosts</a></p>
